data.title: Pizza Ranch in Eau Claire, WI
data.meta_description: Pizza Ranch in Eau Claire is a family-friendly buffet restaurant offering pizza, chicken, salad bar, and desserts. We also offer a full menu for carryout and delivery. Learn more on our site about our menu, hours, pricing, deals, and services available.
data.text:
Pizza Ranch is giving away 100,000 FREE family-sized chocolate chip cookies! Claim yours today by placing a $20+ online order at pizzaranch.com and adding a cookie to your cart from the Deals tab or the dessert menu. Available while supplies last. Other restrictions may apply.
